{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-02016/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-02016"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:20:16"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["backlighting"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man holds a framed photo in his hands as he stands talking to a woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-02016","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-02016"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1/aa40ce15-3f8a-463a-888b-87f1fb03eec2","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:28:38.508Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The drawing behind Alma, a dressmaker’s sketch, features an outline of a figure, who seems to be in motion thanks to the quick linework, along with red and blue patches of colors amidst the otherwise neutral background. It therefore embodies Reynolds’s aesthetics—his passion for bringing to life something dynamic out of raw, inorganic material (as when he invites Countess Henrietta to take her dress for a walk in his atelier). The contrast of colors, too, reminds viewers of the tensions between the protagonists: Alma’s vibrancy and Renolds’s outward coolness.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1176.0132158590309,31.96035242290739,299.4273127753304,487.6872246696036"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1/408be75d-4e70-49c4-90e7-782ed53edf90","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:28:58.722Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In another association with death, Reynolds relates how he and Cyril called their nanny “Black Death.” In this way, Reynolds’s life, upbringing, and house have always been associated with death. His cruelty, it seems, has been present since his youth.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02016/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:983.5022026431718,123.37004405286339,206.62995594713652,239.0859030837004"}}}]}]}]}